'''''Voyages SF'' 9''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[1989]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[A World in Revolt]]" and was written by [[James B. King]].

